'''棘口吸蟲科'''（學名：{{lang|la|Echinostomatidae}}），亦作'''棘口科'''，是[[吸蟲綱|吸蟲綱]][[斜睪目|斜睪目]]之下的一個[[科_(生物)|科]]{{r|WoRMS_108420}}。

==分類==
根據[[ITIS|ITIS]]，本科由19個屬組成<ref name="ITIS_55968">{{ITIS |id=55968 |taxon=Echinostomatidae |access-date=2020-09-12 }}</ref>。這19個屬若按[[WoRMS|WoRMS]]的分類，尚可細分為四個亞科{{r|WoRMS_108420}}，分別如下{{r|Sohn 2011}}：
* [[棘口亚科|棘口亚科]] [[Echinostomatinae|Echinostomatinae]] {{small|Looss, 1899}}
** ''[[Drepanocephalus|Drepanocephalus]]'' {{small|Dietz, 1909}}{{r|Dietz 1909|Sohn 2011}}
** [[棘缘属|棘缘属]] ''{{tsl|en|Echinoparyphium}}'' {{small|Dietz, 1909}}{{r|Dietz 1909|Sohn 2011}}
** [[棘口屬|棘口屬]] ''{{tsl|en|Echinostoma}}'' {{small|Rudolphi, 1809}}<ref name=III>Rudolphi C. A. (1809) ''Entozoorum sive vermium intestinalium, historia naturalis''. Amstelaedami.</ref>：寄生於鳥類及哺乳類（包括人類）動物的腸道內{{r|Sohn 2011}}。
** [[低颈属|低颈属]] ''Hypoderaeum'' {{small|Dietz, 1909}}{{r|Dietz 1909|Sohn 2011}}
** [[似颈属|似颈属]] ''Isthmiophora'' {{small|Lühe, 1909}}：只有陸生和淡水物種。
** ''[[Lyperorchis|Lyperorchis]]'' {{small|Travassos, 1925}}
** [[錐棘屬|錐棘屬]] ''Petasiger'' {{small|Dietz, 1909}}{{r|Dietz 1909|Sohn 2011}}
** ''[[Singhia|Singhia]]'' {{small|Yamaguti, 1958}}
** [[缘口属|缘口属]] ''Paryphostomum'' {{small|Dietz, 1909}}{{r|Dietz 1909}}：被WoRMS認為是錐棘屬的異名。
* 亚科 Nephrostominae {{small|Mendheim, 1943}}
** ''[[Nephrostomum|Nephrostomum]]'' {{small|Dietz, 1909}}{{r|Dietz 1909}}
** [[冠缝属|冠缝属]] ''Patagifer'' {{small|Dietz, 1909}}{{r|Dietz 1909}}
* [[坚体亚科|坚体亚科]] Pegosominae {{small|Odhner, 1910}}
** [[坚体属|坚体属]] ''Pegosomum'' {{small|Ratz, 1903}}，[[钉形属|钉形属]]
* [[柄口亚科|柄口亚科]] Pelmatostominae {{small|Yamaguti, 1958}}
** [[柄口属|柄口属]] ''Pelmatostomum'' {{small|Dietz, 1909}}{{r|Dietz 1909}}<ref name='id10144'>{{cite web| url =http://www.bioinfo.cn/db05/BjdwSpecies.php?action=view&id=10144| title =中形柄口吸虫| work =《中国动物物种编目数据库》| publisher =中国科学院微生物研究所| author =中国科学院动物研究所| accessdate =2009-04-16| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20160305071640/http://www.bioinfo.cn/db05/BjdwSpecies.php?action=view&id=10144| archivedate =2016-03-05}}</ref>
* 亞科地位未定：
** [[达氏属|达氏属]] ''Dietziella'' {{small|Skrjabin & Bashkirova, 1956}}：淡水物種<ref name="WoRMS_1338905">{{WoRMS |id=1338905 |title=''Dietziella'' Skrjabin & Bashkirova, 1956 |last1=Gibson |first1=David |last2=Bray |first2=Rod |access-date=2020-08-27 }}</ref>
** [[新锥棘属|新锥棘属]] ''Neopetasiger'' {{small|Baschkirova, 1941}}
** ''[[Skrjabinophora|Skrjabinophora]]'' {{small|Baschkirova, 1941}}
** ''[[Uroproctepisthmium|Uroproctepisthmium]] {{small|Fischthal & Kuntz, 1976}}

然後，Chai et al. (2009)列出八個屬於本科、分佈於東南亞的屬<ref name=C>{{cite journal |last1=Chai |first1=J. |last2=Shin |first2=E. |last3=Lee |first3=S. |last4=Rim |first4=H. |year=2009 |title=Foodborne Intestinal Flukes in Southeast Asia |journal=''[[The_Korean_Journal_of_Parasitology|The Korean Journal of Parasitology]]'' |volume=47 |issue=Supplementary |pages=69–102 |language=en }}</ref>：
* ''[[Artyfechinostomum|Artyfechinostomum]]'' <small>Lane, 1915</small><ref name=CI>Lane C. 1915. ''Artyfechinostomum sufrartyfex''. A new parasite echinostome of man. ''Indian Journal of Medical Research'', 2, 977–983.</ref>
* [[刺缘属|刺缘属]] ''[[Acanthoparyphium|Acanthoparyphium]]''
* [[棘隙属|棘隙属]] ''Echinochasmus''
* [[棘缘属|棘缘属]] ''{{tsl|en|Echinoparyphium}}'' {{small|Dietz, 1909}}
* [[棘口属|棘口属]] ''{{tsl|en|Echinostoma}}'' {{small|Rudolphi, 1809}}[[
* [[外隙属|外隙属]] ''Episthmium'' <small>Lühe, 1909</small><ref name=CII>Lühe, M. (1909). Parasitische Plattwürmer. I. Trematodes. In: Brauer, A. (Ed.), ''Die Süsswasserfauna Deutschlands. Wine Exkursionfauna''. Jena: Gustav Fischer, 17.</ref>
* [[真缘属|真缘属]] ''[[Euparyphium|Euparyphium]]'' <small>Dietz, 1909</small>{{r|Dietz 1909}}
* [[低颈属|低颈属]] ''[[Hypoderaeum|Hypoderaeum]]'' {{small|Dietz, 1909}}

本科亦曾包括下列各個屬：
* [[中睾属|中睾属]]
* [[刺缘属|刺缘属]] ''[[Acanthoparyphium|Acanthoparyphium]]''
* [[棘隙属|棘隙属]]
* [[鞭带属|鞭带属]]
部分物種後來被劃歸至[[棘隙科|棘隙科]]（[[中睾属|中睾属]]、[[棘隙属|棘隙属]]）及[[鞭带科|鞭带科]]（[[鞭带属|鞭带属]]），但仍屬[[棘口總科|棘口總科]]。

